title: Saoirse Ronan highlights migrant plight at the premiere of Brooklyn - Banburycake.co.uk
text:
Brooklyn star Saoirse Ronan hopes the film's tale of a young Irishwoman in New York will make people more sympathetic towards immigrants. She said: "With everything that's going on now, with the migrant crisis, I think it's really a lovely time for something like this to come out.
